a39fcf806961d504","tid":1647024,"uid":177338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:57:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"de1ae25febaf2efbc7a1e00890891f9ab193ed27","tid":1647024,"uid":35598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:05:02.000Z","msg":"黃東呢啲垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n家下講到明搵到有用淨支那製嘅拎出嚟試到有<br />\n都可以夾硬屈話係示威者插贓嫁禍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1238007375f1ad27cce267aab5811b470b7592c0","tid":1647024,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:30:12.000Z","msg":"大陸整左唔會銷毀佢<br />\n平賣都拎返少少錢<br />\n香港各大2手賣場好多大陸狗賣野<br />\n手痕咪約佢地出黎"}]}